trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailureCollection" /> class is a read-only collection that contains <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailureCollection" /> 類別是包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件的唯讀集合。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在此集合中搜尋的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object is in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 判斷指定的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件是否在這個集合中。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object is in this collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件在此集合中，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="failure" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="failure" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> objects that receives the elements of this collection.
trans-unit.target: 接收此集合項目的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件陣列。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>failures</c> where this method starts copying this collection.
trans-unit.target: <c>failures</c> 中以零起始的索引，這個方法會從此處開始複製這個集合。

trans-unit.source: Copies all <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> objects in this collection to the specified array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 從目標陣列中的指定索引開始，將這個集合中的所有 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件複製到特定陣列。

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫基礎目錄服務導致發生錯誤。

trans-unit.source: The destination array is not large enough, based on the source collection size and the <paramref name="index" /> specified.
trans-unit.target: 根據來源集合大小和指定的 <paramref name="index" />，目的陣列並不夠大。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="failures" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="failures" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 所指定的 <paramref name="index" /> 超出目的陣列範圍。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 要在此集合中搜尋的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 傳回這個集合中指定之 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件第一次出現的索引。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first matching object.
trans-unit.target: 第一個相符物件的以零起始索引。

trans-unit.source: Returns -1 if no member of this collection is identical to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 如果這個集合中沒有成員與 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件相同，則傳回 -1。

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: 呼叫基礎目錄服務導致發生錯誤。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="failure" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="failure" /> 為 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要取得之 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件以零為起始的索引。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個集合中的 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> object that exists at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ReplicationFailure" /> 物件，位在指定的索引。

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 指定的 <paramref name="index" /> 超出集合範圍。
